snippet.title: Princess Peach: Showtime! - Nintendo Direct 9.14.2023
snippet.description:
Princess Peach: Showtime! is releasing for Nintendo Switch on March 22, 2024! Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/princess-peach-showtime-switch/

The wicked Grape and the Sour Bunch have taken over the Sparkle Theater, and now it's up to Peach and the theater's guardian Stella to save the play––and the day!

Peach can transform and use fantastic showstopping abilities to face off against the Sour Bunch.

#PrincessPeachShowtime #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect
